<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bsẖwq wḥnyn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (bsẖwq wḥnyn wṣbr snyn .. bkl yqyn wạ̹ymạn
 llsmạ sẖạkẖṣyn wmntẓryn .. nsẖwfk bạlʿyạn)2
 ạlqrạr- (wtnạhy̱ ạllyl tnạhy̱ .. wtqạrb ạlnhạr
 wʿrysnạ jạy yạkẖdnạ .. nstwṭn ạldyạr)2
 2-(yạ gẖrbẗ kẖlạṣ dạrt ạlạ̉yạm .. wywmnạ dh msẖ hyʿwd
 bạnt ạlʿlạmạt hạnt ạlṣʿwbạt .. mạ ạ̉ḥly̱ ạlywm ạlmwʿwd)2
 3-(nṣʿd bhtạf wbṣwt ạlbwq .. wmsyḥnạ ylạqynạ
 ngẖny ʿly̱ ṭwl nhtf wnqwl .. mjdaⁿạ lk yạ fạdynạ)2
 4-(ậmyn tʿạl yạ ḥbybnạ tʿạl .. ạ̉rwạḥnạ btnạdyk
 ḥqq wʿdk ạ̹bsṭ lṭfk .. dh sẖʿbk mstnyk)2</lyrics>
<author>bạsyly nsym, bạsyly nsym</author>
<hymn_number>4902</hymn_number>
</song>